1) Set the new tests in config/*.test
and check the generation command with ./setup/gencmd

2) Test locally with ./setup/run

3) Submit references with ./setup/submit_reference

------------------------------
wait jobs to finish
------------------------------

4) Collect references with ./setup/makeavg

5) Update references with ./setup/update_ref_plot

6) Update main test configuration file with ./setup/config_setup

7) Update all tests dcube configuration files with ./setup/update_dcube_xml

8) svn commit test/HepMCAnalysis_i_TestConfiguration.xml
and make a new tag
